#subtitle: Paramilitary organizing in defense of the republic.

= Reichsbanner

The *Ruhrarbeiterverteidigungsbund*, or simply Verteidigungsbund, is a mass organization for the defense of the Ruhr workers against the police and far-right extremists who threaten their protests. Some would call it a paramilitary, although currently it is hardly any sort of military. It is officially associated with the leftist parties - the SPD and SP, but by far the largest component is with the SPD.

[? if workers_spd < 46 or workers_spd < (workers_dvlp + workers_dkp) or workers_spd < workers_sp : The Reichsbanner is having a more difficult time recruiting, as the SPD is no longer the dominant party among the workers. Many of its members have left. ?]

- @militant: Fund more military-style training and equipment for the Verteidigungsbund.
- @militant_2: Use our existing resources to support more training for the Verteidigungsbund.
- @same: Keep the Verteidigungsbund as it is.
- @cut_rb: Cut funding for the Verteidigungsbund.
